        </item>
        <item>
            <title>日本女仆咖啡厅引入 AI 翻译荧幕，支援百种语言、助外国游客体验「萌文化」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/ai-translation-in-maid-cafe/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-translation-in-maid-cafe</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/ai-translation-in-maid-cafe/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 10:56:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293957</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日本秋叶原的女仆咖啡厅凭借独特「萌文化」吸引世界各地游客，但语言障碍常令外国顾客无法尽享体验。科技公司 Pixie Dust Technologies 开发「VUEVO Display 透明翻译萤幕」，并于 at-home cafe 试用，可消除沟通隔阂，令顾客沉浸于与女仆互动的欢乐氛围。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293963" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/703612426a77a6194145-694x462.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/703612426a77a6194145-694x462.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/703612426a77a6194145.jpeg 959w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：Yahoo</p><p>源自筑波大学的创新企业 Pixie Dust Technologies 推出 VUEVO Display，支援超过 100 种语言即时翻译。装置透过透明萤幕显示字幕，如同观赏电影时的字幕般自然流畅，让顾客毋须低头查看手机即可与女仆顺畅交流。透明设计保证双方视线无阻，顾客得以清晰观察女仆表情与动作，体验中视觉与情感互动融为一体。针对如「萌萌哒」等日语特有词汇，萤幕会显示「MOEMOE」，既保留语言本身的趣味，又增添互动亲切感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293964" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b25a443c61bc81969cb2-694x449.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="449" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b25a443c61bc81969cb2-694x449.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b25a443c61bc81969cb2.jpeg 959w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：Yahoo</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293961" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/f30fb6db70a3467f9954-694x470.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="470" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/f30fb6db70a3467f9954-694x470.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/f30fb6db70a3467f9954.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：SCMP</p><p>at-home cafe 现于东京及大阪合共经营 10 家分店。随著赴日旅客人数回升，东京分店外国顾客占比约 10% 至 15%，当中以亚洲游客为主。店方虽已提供英语菜单和基本词汇表，亦有安排女仆接受英语训练，惟角色扮演中的用语常超出一般教材范围。女仆一句「请让我为您施加魔法，使这道蛋包饭变得更美味！」既带戏剧感，亦充满情境魅力，传统翻译方式难以完美诠释语气与氛围，VUEVO Display 则有效弥补此不足，使外国顾客能融入整体体验之中。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293962" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/3906aa7c6f19488685b7-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/3906aa7c6f19488685b7-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/3906aa7c6f19488685b7.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：SCMP</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293960" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2422299c405442c694e6-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2422299c405442c694e6-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2422299c405442c694e6.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：SCMP</p><p>初步试用结果反应热烈。顾客认为装置操作简便，有助打破语言屏障，且不影响互动乐趣。at-home cafe 营运团队期望借助技术强化服务，让不同国籍的游客亲身感受到日本独树一帜的「萌文化」魅力。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://zh.cn.nikkei.com/trend/cool-japan/57979-2025-02-10-05-00-10.html">日经中文</a>、<a href="https://www.scmp.com/news/people-culture/article/3299145/japan-maid-cafe-uses-ai-translate-conversations-100-languages-enhancing-service">SCMP</a>、<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BF%BB%E8%AD%AF%E5%8A%A9%E6%94%BB%E9%80%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%83%95%E5%92%96%E5%95%A1%E5%BB%B3-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%90%8C%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E6%9C%80%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%9D%E6%8B%9C-033014442.html">JapHub</a>、<a href="https://soranews24.com/2025/02/21/foreigner-friendly-maid-cafe-adds-translation-panels-to-akihabara-location/">Sora News</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
