        <item>
            <title>Apple 在美投资逾 5000 亿美元，拓展人工智能、创造数千职位</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/apple-will-spend-more-than-500-billion-in-the-u-s-over-the-next-four-years/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-will-spend-more-than-500-billion-in-the-u-s-over-the-next-four-years</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/25/apple-will-spend-more-than-500-billion-in-the-u-s-over-the-next-four-years/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 25 Feb 2025 07:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293915</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 今日发表新闻稿宣布计划于未来四年在美国投资超过 5,000 亿美元（约港币 3.9 万亿元），推动美国制造业发展，同时强化人工智能、晶片工程等创新领域。Apple 指计划可与全美 50 个州的供应商紧密合作，创造数千个工作岗位。Apple 行政总裁 Tim Cook 表示，Apple 对美国创新充满信心，期望投资可扩大当地经济效益，惠及民生，巩固 Apple 在全球科技领域中的领先地位。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293923" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentaus-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentaus-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentaus-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Apple 计划于德州候斯顿建设一座 250,000 平方呎先进制造设施，专门生产支援 Apple Intelligence 的伺服器。预计新工厂可在 2026 年投入运作，料可创造数千个就业机会，显著推动当地经济。Apple 指这项投资有望吸引相关产业链上下游企业进驻，令区域经济有所提升。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293924" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentsem-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentsem-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentsem-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Apple 供应商德州仪器位于犹他州的新的半导体制造厂</p><p>公司同时计划扩增美国先进制造基金（US Advanced Manufacturing Fund）金额一倍，从 50 亿美元（约港币 388.75 亿元）增加至 100 亿美元（约港币 777.5 亿元），用于促进全国的先进制造业和技能发展，提升本土制造业实力，为美国制造业注入新活力。Apple 希望能够加强供应链，减少依赖海外生产，确保产品能稳定供应市场，同时响应当地对本土生产的需求。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293925" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmenttex-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmenttex-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmenttex-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Apple 供应商德州仪器位于犹他州的新的半导体制造厂</p><p>为培养产业后备人才，Apple 将于密歇根州底特律开办制造学院，为学生与工人提供实务培训。学院与密歇根州立大学（Michigan State University）合作，课程涵盖机械工程、自动化生产、数据分析等领域，以培养新一代技术专才。Apple 希望提升美国劳动力素质，亦让当地社区青年能学以致用，实现职业生涯上的突围与发展。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestment4ht-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestment4ht-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestment4ht.jpg 980w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>为应对数码经济持续扩张的趋势，Apple 计划扩建资料中心及 Apple Intelligence 基础设施，以支援与日俱增的服务需求。公司亦将在 20 个州制作 Apple TV+ 节目，扩展其内容生态系统，既满足用户多元化的娱乐需求，又促进美国影视产业繁荣发展。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293926" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmenttex-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmenttex-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmenttex-1.jpg 980w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Apple 供应商德州仪器位于犹他州的新的半导体制造厂</p><p>Tim Cook 指出，Apple 在美国现已支持逾 290 万个职位，涵盖直接雇用、供应链合作及 iOS 应用程式开发等多元领域。此次大规模投资体现 Apple 推动美国经济与技术创新的决心，冀望为当地社区带来长远裨益，实现双赢局面。Tim Cook 补充，Apple 将持续专注于可持续发展，确保在推动经济增长的同时，不忘守护环境与社会责任。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293922" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentinf-581x580.jpg" alt="" width="581" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentinf-581x580.jpg 581w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentinf-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/appleusinvestmentinf.jpg 653w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 581px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2025/02/apple-will-spend-more-than-500-billion-usd-in-the-us-over-the-next-four-years/">Apple Newsroom</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
